  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">FUAD - Funding for humanitarian aid for internally displaced persons in UN run camp</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will bring about significant change to the lives of those in Mosul, Iraq who have fled conflict as a result of the military operation to retake Mosul from ISIL control.  
Christian Aid has been in constant communication with the WFP in order to avoid duplication and fill gaps.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To provide life-saving assistance to 548 newly arrived households in Al Alam. 
This will be achieved through the distribution of food packages in line with WFP family food ration baskets providing 1841 calories per person per day for 30 days.</narrative>
  </description>
